    "description": "<p>Here at Ebb &amp; Flow Group, we’re fuelled by an honest love for good food and extraordinary experiences – through carefully sourced ingredients, immaculately curated spaces, and a deep-rooted commitment to the art of culinary storytelling.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We’re simple people with a simple ethos—to use food that is good for the ecosystem. We work with smaller, sustainable farms and specialty boutiques to procure the most intentional and ethically-sourced produce. Supplemented by our relentless drive to advance food innovation and digitalisation – what you get are unique dining experiences, enjoyed in the comfort of your own home or in our spaces.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our team believes in fast and focused execution – done is always better than perfect.</p>\n<p>A great work ethic, intellectual curiosity and a willingness to learn are at the core of our team – if you don’t work hard and ask the right questions, your competitors will.</p>\n<p>We’re convinced that the best ideas should always win – no matter whether they come from an intern or the CEO.</p>",
